OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Oil giant BP has rejected calls for a  
OL,6, windfall tax on energy companies'      
OL,7, bumper profits, saying it would reduce 
OL,8, investment in UK gas and renewables.   
OL,10,FBP posted a profit of $12.8bn (#9.5bn) 
OL,11,Ffor 2021 after oil and gas prices      
OL,12,Fsurged in the second half of the year. 
OL,14,FThat has prompted calls for a one-off  
OL,15,Ftax to help support families struggling
OL,16,Fto pay their energy bills.             
OL,18,FLabour said it was "only fair and      
OL,19,Fright" that energy firms making higher 
OL,20,Fprofits should pay more tax.           
